(10895, 937, 'team_description', 'You shot a movie or youre about to make one.  You wrote a book. You have an event. A message. A product. Maybe all of the above.Now you need to sell.  A ticket, a book, an idea.  You want the right audiences.  Hmm, are you sitting down? As it happens, no ones waiting to hear from you. \r\n\r\nJournalists are busy and your potential consumers have infinite options.Media, meanwhile, is a supernova:  in a million pieces as the universe continues to expand. You want to go where the people are. Where they watch, read, think, engage . . . where they post, tweet, like, and stay in touch.\r\n\r\nWe can help you get there--where messages meet eyeballs, where goals meet bottom lines.'),
(10896, 937, '_team_description', 'field_58be339080008'),
(10897, 937, 'team_0_image', '907'),
(10898, 937, '_team_0_image', 'field_58be26dbd5a67'),
(10899, 937, 'team_0_name', 'Nancy Lovell'),
(10900, 937, '_team_0_name', 'field_58be26f1d5a68'),
(10901, 937, 'team_0_role', 'Partner'),
(10902, 937, '_team_0_role', 'field_58be26f8d5a69'),
(10903, 937, 'team_0_bio', 'A millennium, no, 15 years ago, Julie Fairchild and I separately went on our own and, since days alone can get long, thought we might share an office.  The physical office space never materialized, but inside a year, an LLP did.\r\n \r\nIn that company of two, I expected wed attract employees on their way to bigger things. What did I know? Our niche work is far more than widgets, and Lovell-Fairchild grew into an enviable team of professionals whom we\'ve seen grow into experts in what they do. \r\n \r\nIn our strategic-communications work, I lean into the communications part, urging our team, on one level, to spell canceled with one l, and, regardless of AP Stylebook, to use hopefully to mean what it says. More generally, in framing, messaging, media training, writing, pitches . . . I help shape client needs into news.'),
(10904, 937, '_team_0_bio', 'field_5931ba112e426'),
(10905, 937, 'team_1_image', '903'),
(10906, 937, '_team_1_image', 'field_58be26dbd5a67'),
(10907, 937, 'team_1_name', 'Julie Fairchild'),
(10908, 937, '_team_1_name', 'field_58be26f1d5a68'),
(10909, 937, 'team_1_role', 'Partner'),
(10910, 937, '_team_1_role', 'field_58be26f8d5a69'),
(10911, 937, 'team_1_bio', 'You tell your story, and I see it unfold in living color--including its potential to make the world a better place. Does that sound cheesy? My mom will tell you its in my DNA to look for what matters, poking and prodding for the right place to build a bridge between where you are and where you want to be. All the while, Im mentally skimming my Rolodex for new friends you need to know who complement your cause with theirs.  Im dogged (some say stubborn) and refuse to accept any result but the best. Because its your babyand we spread the word about goodness for a higher purpose.\r\n \r\nWhen not working, Im browsing an estate sale for treasures or enjoying my wildflowers in the Texas Hill Country with my chuck-wagon cooking husband, Rick, our four-grown children, and our ever-expanding family and friends, who keep me laughing.'),
(10912, 937, '_team_1_bio', 'field_5931ba112e426'),
(10913, 937, 'team_2_image', '906'),
(10914, 937, '_team_2_image', 'field_58be26dbd5a67'),
(10915, 937, 'team_2_name', 'Monique Sondag'),
(10916, 937, '_team_2_name', 'field_58be26f1d5a68'),
(10917, 937, 'team_2_role', 'Vice President of Operations'),
(10918, 937, '_team_2_role', 'field_58be26f8d5a69'),
(10919, 937, 'team_2_bio', 'I look at something and ask myself how I could organize it. Whether a spreadsheet, a kitchen pantry, or chapstick and candy bars at the checkout, my mind is trained to bring order. I was nine years old, at a friend\'s house to play, and instead organizing her closet. Her mom offered to take us to see a Disney movie. I passed on the ticket to continue in my version of a playdate. \r\n\r\nA decade ago, I met Lovell and Fairchild. A decade later the conversation hasn\'t stopped. Lovell-Fairchild Communications has been a place to exercise all my organizational quirks from creating campaign flows, to orchestrating events of all sorts, to synchronizing the many plates that need to spin for any given project. My mission is to help people, clients and projects alike create white space to think and breathe. \r\n\r\nOtherwise you\'ll find me personally thinking, breathing, painting, cooking, reading, on the hunt for the perfect Old Fashioned, or spending time with people who make me laugh.'),
(10920, 937, '_team_2_bio', 'field_5931ba112e426'),
(10921, 937, 'team_3_image', '904'),
(10922, 937, '_team_3_image', 'field_58be26dbd5a67'),
