(12890, 989, 'testimonial_slides_0_slide', '"We all know that people must hear about books before they will buy books. When I wrote my book: Things I Wish Id Known Before We Got Married, it was Lovell-Fairchild Communications who got the word out for me. Hundreds of thousands of young couples have now been helped because they heard; they bought; they read. I highly recommend Lovell-Fairchild Communications.'),
(12891, 989, '_testimonial_slides_0_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
