(13686, 994, 'testimonial_slides_2_slide', '"I have found Lovell-Fairchild to be insightful and strategic counselors who bring a high level of professional integrity and creativity to their work. As one of the few agencies in the faith-based niche, I have known Lovell-Fairchild to be world class media planners with extensive press contacts that have proven invaluable to the Potter\'s House over the years. They are excellent partners who bring a great deal of thoughtfulness, big picture thinking, and tireless execution to every assignment."'),
