(15888, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_0_slide', '"We all know that people must hear about books before they will buy books. When I wrote my book: Things I Wish Id Known Before We Got Married, it was Lovell-Fairchild Communications who got the word out for me. Hundreds of thousands of young couples have now been helped because they heard; they bought; they read. I highly recommend Lovell-Fairchild Communications.'),
(15889, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_0_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15890, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_0_author', 'Gary Chapman, <br>Ph.D. author of The Five Love Languages.'),
(15891, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_0_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(15892, 1005, 'testimonial_slides', '10'),
(15893, 1005, '_testimonial_slides', 'field_595d618c0fa55'),
(15894, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_1_slide', '"Lovell-Fairchild has amassed the best reputation across the Christian media that I have ever seen, and they command a professional respect from the media, churches, and parachurch ministries across this nation. They have deep networks, they are creative, trustworthy, and know how to tell your story while keeping it your story."'),
(15895, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_1_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15896, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_1_author', 'Duane Gaylord, <br>Sr. VP Billy Graham Evangelistic Association and Samaritans Purse'),
(15897, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_1_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(15898, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_2_slide', '"I have found Lovell-Fairchild to be insightful and strategic counselors who bring a high level of professional integrity and creativity to their work. As one of the few agencies in the faith-based niche, I have known Lovell-Fairchild to be world class media planners with extensive press contacts that have proven invaluable to the Potter\'s House over the years. They are excellent partners who bring a great deal of thoughtfulness, big picture thinking, and tireless execution to every assignment."'),
(15899, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_2_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15900, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_2_author', 'Bishop T. D. Jakes'),
(15901, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_2_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(15902, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_3_slide', '"I have worked with Lovell-Fairchild Communications for over 10 years to promote and market a variety of books, films and other projects. I have found them to be people of integrity who came along side us and helped us deliver our projects to the market with excellence. They are a one stop shop for promotion and marketing; with a variety of skilled professionals and I would wholeheartedly endorse them to anyone who needs public relations or marketing support. Nancy Lovell and Julie Fairchild and their team of professionals are some of the best people I have ever worked with".'),
(15903, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_3_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15904, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_3_author', 'Jim McBride, <br>Executive Producer, Sherwood Pictures'),
(15905, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_3_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(15906, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_4_slide', '"Their network and know-how were great assets to our efforts. Their staff diligently executed and moved fast to capitalize on emerging opportunities." Andrea Lee, Winshape Foundation\r\n"I cannot imagine opening a movie without Lovell-Fairchild. They bring so much more than publicity. They bring wise counsel, a flawless work ethic, and perhaps most importantly, a great sense of camaraderie and humor to the crushing workload of a feature film. There are a number of agencies that claim strength in the faith space, but not one can hold a candle to Lovell Fairchild."'),
(15907, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_4_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15908, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_4_author', 'Kris Fuhr, <br>Provident Films'),
(15909, 1005, '_testimonial_slides_4_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(15910, 1005, 'testimonial_slides_5_slide', '"I am impressed by the quality of their work, but even more-so by their personal commitment to us as clients."'),
