(17119, 1030, 'testimonial_slides_4_slide', '"Their network and know-how were great assets to our efforts. Their staff diligently executed and moved fast to capitalize on emerging opportunities." Andrea Lee, Winshape Foundation\r\n"I cannot imagine opening a movie without Lovell-Fairchild. They bring so much more than publicity. They bring wise counsel, a flawless work ethic, and perhaps most importantly, a great sense of camaraderie and humor to the crushing workload of a feature film. There are a number of agencies that claim strength in the faith space, but not one can hold a candle to Lovell Fairchild."'),
