(184, 1, '2017-04-09 18:15:48', '2017-04-09 18:15:48', 'Award-winning radio personality, author, wit, storyteller . . . riveting speaker and more, Brant Hansen connects audiences to the heart the story. Multiple-time winner of national "Personality of the Year" awards, Brant currently reaches more than 2 million people through his radio show, syndicated on more than 200 stations. A skeptic who came to faith, Brant is equally engaging for general and faith audiences. Given his passion for people in need, Brant is designated storyteller for CURE International, which facilitates medical treatment and spiritual encouragement across 30 countries for children with disabilities.', 'Brant Hansen', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brant-hansen', '', '', '2017-06-01 22:21:06', '2017-06-01 22:21:06', '', 0, 'http://lovell-fairchild.dev//?post_type=clients&#038;p=184', 25, 'clients', '', 0),
